headline: Exxon Mobil: $55 Brent is Fine; Open to M&A, Including Permian
summary: Jack Williams, senior vice president at Exxon Mobil, said the energy major is in “fighting weight” to weather the downturn as it looks for more opportunities to add value.

headline: ICE Hits 52-Week High, Trades at a Discount: How to Play the Stock
summary: Intercontinental rides on data services growth, mortgage network strength, and strategic buyouts, though rising expenses may weigh on near-term margins.
